{"tid":2415622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華春瑩遭網民恥笑　明知故問：中國人為何不能用Facebook？","createTime":"2021-02-20T11:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T11:54:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6830fde942ad79818a78be122b7d1cd0fa1c9f6e","tid":2415622,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ugwBnm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ugwBnm.png&h=f35142c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於華春瑩這番話明顯與事實以及一般人的認知不相符，隨即引來海內外輿論熱議。法廣網甚至以「似乎很天真」來形容華春瑩提出的一連串反問。<br />\n<br />\n不少內地網站對其發言亦很吃驚，在「品蔥」網站有網民寫道：「爆笑如雷了，華春瑩質問美國，為甚麼中國人就不可以用推特，臉書呢？」「我也想問啊，為甚麼中國人就不可以使用推特和臉書啊？」「黨和國家是為了人民好，不讓他們受西方文化的侵襲。你怎麼就不懂呢？修牆也是為了普通人好。」「上推特被關八個月的那幾個尋釁滋事罪不知道放出來沒有？」<br />\n<br />\n還有網民反問：「說得好像牆是別人建的一樣」「所以華春瑩，趙立堅，耿爽，所有你推特臉書見到的五毛粉紅都不是中國人？！」「不小心說漏嘴了這是」。"},{"pid":"b1edf25b0d7bbf7572a9f83be129e1aa150c9225","tid":2415622,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210220/TA5PGU4QFNAN3O3HNCPKHTFEQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210220%2FTA5PGU4QFNAN3O3HNCPKHTFEQQ%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=ad37883b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210220%2FTA5PGU4QFNAN3O3HNCPKHTFEQQ%2F&h=13264091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210220/TA5PGU4QFNAN3O3HNCPKHTFEQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"5b12316245dcb577c9ff738267274e02514b3ca7","tid":2415622,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly6XwYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy6XwYh.jpg&h=f390d92f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ce2bd3f6b901b8b4e636b16d61ffc046485d019","tid":2415622,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c